{"tid":1323274,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老文宣]第二戰場係電台呀","createTime":"2019-07-16T07:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:17:04.000Z","uid":264079,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"3e09e9d166ec8b3d6292dac9d0cea0bc59366662","tid":1323274,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"老老實實而家聽得電台嘅都係一班上咗年紀人士，文宣下一個目標，一定係霸哂電台節目嘅phone-in 時間，原因有四 <br />\nif you can&rsquo;t beat them join them (講緊媒體渠道)<br />\n<br />\n一。 大部分聽收音機嘅都係上咗年紀嘅人(當中𣎴乏淺藍，深藍，淺黃)，既然未必阻到佢哋夜晚睇cctvb吸收維穩資訊，佢哋上下晝係會開收音機做BGM，所以電台起到一定文宣作用，一定要用電台講返事實出嚟，如黑驚點打人，擾民，制衡返cctvb<br />\n<br />\n二。好多商戶無電視都會開收音機，文宣效果可擴大至戶客群<br />\n<br />\n三。大部分港台，商台節目主持都係黃底，會幫拖<br />\n<br />\n四。啲廢老懶得睇圖/字，講埋俾佢哋聽就最好，仲可以擺archive 上Facebook 重溫<br />\n<br />\n主力:<br />\n1.政府唔回應五大訴求<br />\n2.追究黑驚濫權(拍淋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，擾民<br />\n3.鬧返建制狗嘉賓<br />\n<br />\n以下電台節目都可以phone in 按時間<br />\n<br />\n商台雷霆881<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ErFUjvy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErFUjvy.png&h=17452bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在晴朗的一天出發<br />\n星期一至五 08:00-10:00<br />\n電話1872881<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港電台第一台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFYVOoY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFYVOoY.png&h=ac11b3e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千禧年代<br />\n星期一至五 08:00-10:00<br />\n電話1872311<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港電台第一台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pT7vChn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpT7vChn.png&h=2a0e38c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自由風自由phone<br />\n星期一至五 17:00-20:00<br />\n電話1872311<br />\n<br />\n一陣好同我打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28acb3b1216f892aa58f2597b9be096d82441e7","tid":1323274,"uid":761,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a>"},{"pid":"c712000e74a9c5f322307dcef27d5a3a16ddb397","tid":1323274,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:50:48.000Z","msg":"明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a>"},{"pid":"1be728538ebbe8cb90ac3ef97f1b0dc644cab69e","tid":1323274,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48d8344a3a66658649e20c42da271978fc4b40cb","tid":1323274,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"Gogogo"},{"pid":"1cd2c283b3ec9a728d2f591824cef82c15ff3a31","tid":1323274,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:12:46.000Z","msg":"開波啦"},{"pid":"f1b504221f67fa6ced52ecf1fc621563d4e5f503","tid":1323274,"uid":243198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21baff459ca05c9fbb621705baafb4c8bbbeab18","tid":1323274,"uid":74958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"好多的士司機都會聽，可以潛移默化咁洗佢地腦"},{"pid":"aea6a5c77feab3396fa44ecb49560269f0c5ef82","tid":1323274,"uid":267757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:18:04.000Z","