IZE}\" /><br />\n千禧年代<br />\n星期一至五 08:00-10:00<br />\n電話1872311<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港電台第一台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pT7vChn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpT7vChn.png&h=2a0e38c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自由風自由phone<br />\n星期一至五 17:00-20:00<br />\n電話1872311<br />\n<br />\n一陣好同我打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"邊個再講叫班狗從良同我入來<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324459</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"43e9be16d1a474b36396e1b6d4bf0c1d34e411f8","tid":1323274,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a542f51f263ecf8308f5c8465559d0d7902f4194","tid":1323274,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"儲力5點"},{"pid":"4b831a0448d5051523402886e685f01837d7d221","tid":1323274,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3b1e29928e634bfb1606da4a20d0d68c9387c6b","tid":1323274,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4a8cf57dc331f102ba4c88a19b6680ebdfd364e","tid":1323274,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"4224611781350bebac22ac18c540a8cefe79293a","tid":1323274,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"Gogogo"},{"pid":"9fad2753b2f2b1ebb27eea3f1afe5d433ddf1bb4","tid":1323274,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:52:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}